{"tid":1887316,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"本土研究社：【隔離營隱藏選項：洞梓警察渡假屋】","createTime":"2020-02-19T12:25:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-19T14:35:19.000Z","uid":344792,"like":40,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"3936ef7b4a862016f71c8ea6d346428504929a3e","tid":1887316,"uid":344792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T12:25:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/244689185627162/posts/2857517354344319/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F244689185627162%2Fposts%2F2857517354344319%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=lLWZrBwjloX75B4v2mFt5DXucVKzxOX0ld4zZjK7Pao%3D&h=e6ae600e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/244689185627162/posts/2857517354344319/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n研究員剛在田野考察過程中，發現有個隱世渡假營相當適合做隔離營，叫洞梓警察渡假屋，請大家幫手推介一下。<br />\n<br />\n渡假屋位處大埔洞梓路到盡頭，人煙稀少，營內屋與屋間隔適中，每間渡假屋都上千呎，廚房廁所、燒烤爐、娛樂設施一應俱全，之前還有麻雀供應，面對大埔慈山寺觀音像景，風水好過火神山，相當適合做隔離營。<br />\n<br />\n不要被官方資料影響，誤以為裡面只得5間度假大屋可租【註一】，做隔離營空間有限。實地可見，其實另一邊重收埋左十多個門牌 (B1-B5、B8-B12及C2-C5)大屋，長期丟空，又唔翻新，現時放在可供短租政府土地表無人問津。<br />\n<br />\n翻查官方紀錄，揭示該度假營亦曾於2014年用作跨部門伊波拉病毒防疫演習，與當時與鯉魚門公園同時被徵用作模擬感染病毒後的防疫訓練。【註二】現時鯉魚門公園已被徵用作隔離營，但警察度假屋卻依然固我。<br />\n<br />\n去年警隊還為渡假屋重開舉辦過一場度假屋命名大賽，最後得獎名稱叫梓藍、梓樂、梓然、梓雅及梓和【註三】，反映了現時警隊的創意水平。如果徵用做隔離營，大家又會幫佢改個咩名?<br />\n<br />\n其實政府連自己設施都未善用好，又不肯全面封關，就要徵用社區公屋戶埋單，根本說不過去，應倡議立即徵用度假營及翻新丟空度假屋做隔離營，相關部門亦不要在疫情當前還漠視未善用官地。<br />\n<br />\n#田野考察<br />\n#未善用官地<br />\n#洞梓警察渡假屋<br />\n#渡假屋叫梓樂<br />\n#虧你重住得落<br />\n<br />\n--<br />\n【註一】《警聲》- 健康生活：洞梓警察度假屋重新開放<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.police.gov.hk/offbeat/1129/chi/7661.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.police.gov.hk%2Foffbeat%2F1129%2Fchi%2F7661.html&d=lLWZrBwjloX75B4v2mFt5DXucVKzxOX0ld4zZjK7Pao%3D&h=f91e1708\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.police.gov.hk/offbeat/1129/chi/7661.html</a><br />\n<br />\n【註二】2015年衛生防護中心《通訊》第三十六期 p.7<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.chp.gov.hk/files/pdf/chp36_en.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chp.gov.hk%2Ffiles%2Fpdf%2Fchp36_en.pdf&d=lLWZrBwjloX75B4v2mFt5DXucVKzxOX0ld4zZjK7Pao%3D&h=b2b4c313\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.chp.gov.hk/files/pdf/chp36_en.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n【註三】《警聲》- 簡訊：洞梓警察度假屋命名比賽頒獎典禮<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.police.gov.hk/offbeat/1132/chi/7813.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.police.gov.hk%2Foffbeat%2F1132%2Fchi%2F7813.html&d=lLWZrBwjloX75B4v2mFt5DXucVKzxOX0ld4zZjK7Pao%3D&h=2361658c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.police.gov.hk/offbeat/1132/chi/7813.html</a><br />\n<br />\n--<br />\n💰挖多啲地　支持民間土地研究：<br />\n<a href=\"https://liber-research.com/research-category/land-supply/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fliber-research.com%2Fresearch-category%2Fland-supply%2F&d=lLWZrBwjloX75B4v2mFt5DXucVKzxOX0ld4zZjK7Pao%3D&h=ce9ad7c0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://liber-research.com/research-category/land-supply/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u4PYdWE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu4PYdWE.jpg&h=6c7813d8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6gDBK3k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6gDBK3k.jpg&h=340cf7d0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vHTVf91.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvHTVf91.jpg&h=18e729a4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WsfXuu2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWsfXuu2.jpg&h=78e8ac00&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Hx9EHP2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHx9EHP2.jpg&h=d1e119ec&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oJEA0BJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoJEA0BJ.jpg&h=97e909d9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"64ea05d33866783cb36d8f5859608480c2814781","tid":1887316,"uid":30836,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"cite